00:12:09.180 --> 00:12:10.608
di religye?

00:12:10.294 --> 00:12:12.378
nisht getshepet gornisht.

00:12:13.230 --> 00:12:14.827
alts iz gevezn, UNK,

00:12:15.019 --> 00:12:16.937
mentshn flegn geyn in shul?

00:12:17.466 --> 00:12:19.251
onheyb, di ershte tsayt

00:12:19.251 --> 00:12:20.936
zenen mentshn gegan in shul.

00:12:21.280 --> 00:12:25.712
ober shpeter UNK zenen shoyn di kinder, di yunge, shoyn nisht gegangen,

00:12:26.460 --> 00:12:30.841
vayl ⟨az⟩ zey, m'hot zey gezogt, az zey zenen Pyonern, torn zey nisht geyn, gleybn in RELIGION.

00:12:30.865 --> 00:12:33.108
di eltere mentshn hobn nokh gegleybt,

00:12:33.278 --> 00:12:36.799
ober di kinder, m'hot, hobn shoyn moyre gehat tsu geyn in di shkoles.

00:12:38.644 --> 00:12:40.359
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn

00:12:40.821 --> 00:12:43.819
di milkhome, iz, zuntik in der fri...

00:12:44.196 --> 00:12:49.691
lomir zikh tsukern a bisl tsurik, yene tsayt, far der milkhome, beys s'zaynen shoyn gekumen di sovyetn.

00:12:49.191 --> 00:12:50.096
yo.

00:12:49.967 --> 00:12:55.833
zogt mir, vu ir hot gelebt, zaynen dortn gevezn yidn velkhe m'hot aroysgeshikt, oder tsugenumen?

00:12:56.886 --> 00:12:59.057
ven di rusn zenen arayngekumen,

00:12:59.299 --> 00:13:02.735
hobn zey genumen ve-, vemen ⟨m'hot zey⟩ geklert az zey zenen raykhe.

00:13:03.197 --> 00:13:05.891
hot men zey aroysgeshikt f- keyn Sibir.

00:13:06.538 --> 00:13:09.400
ir gedenkt azelkhe mentshn, ⟨zey hot ge-⟩ zey gekent?

00:13:09.340 --> 00:13:12.388
s'iz geven eyner vos er hot gehat a yatke, katsovim.

00:13:12.613 --> 00:13:15.526
hot men zey aroysgeshikt, un tsurik zenen zey shoyn nisht gekumen.

00:13:16.292 --> 00:13:18.179
un m'hot aroysgeshikt nokh yidn,

00:13:18.179 --> 00:13:21.112
vos zey hobn gehat a olearnye vos m'hot gemakht OIL.

00:13:21.355 --> 00:13:23.138
hobn shoyn oykhet nisht tsurikgekumen.

00:13:23.329 --> 00:13:25.933
un eyner vos er fleg hobn a g- a kleytl,

00:13:25.933 --> 00:13:28.571
a kleyn kleytl; zey hobn aleyn gearbet, di yidn.

00:13:28.594 --> 00:13:30.123
hot men zey oykhet farshikt,

00:13:30.889 --> 00:13:33.009
un tsurik zenen shoyn keyns nisht gekumen.

00:13:33.623 --> 00:13:38.496
zogt mir, zaynen gevezn, hot ir gehert yene tsayt vegn tsienistn, y⟨u⟩dishistn,

00:13:38.496 --> 00:13:40.620
oder andere farsheydene,

00:13:40.879 --> 00:13:43.556
 organizatsyes oder partyes?

00:13:42.651 --> 00:13:47.387
bay undz in shtetl iz geven a organizatsye, dos hot geheysn ⟨a BEJTARO-⟩ Betar.

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:49.479
Zhabotinski's.

00:13:50.278 --> 00:13:52.499
mayn bruder iz geven der MEFAKED.

00:13:53.130 --> 00:13:55.857
me fleg kumen, me fleg tantsn. s'iz geven nokh

00:13:56.016 --> 00:13:57.309
a Khaluts,

00:13:57.400 --> 00:13:59.329
un s'iz geven Shomer Hatsair.

00:13:59.329 --> 00:14:02.558
azoy flegn zikh tsunandkumen di yugnt. me fleg zingen

00:14:02.563 --> 00:14:03.724
un tantsn,

00:14:03.724 --> 00:14:06.197
un m'hot gehat redes, un m'hot geredt,

00:14:06.197 --> 00:14:07.738
m'hot geleyent bikhlekh.

00:14:08.487 --> 00:14:11.738
zaynen gevezn bay aykh, Bundistn oykh? neyn?

00:14:12.790 --> 00:14:14.556
neyn. UNK.

00:14:13.212 --> 00:14:15.889
ir hot onteyl genumen in di

00:14:15.912 --> 00:14:19.787
batrefenish fun di yugnt, VOT fun... ir zayt nit geven keyn,

00:14:19.962 --> 00:14:22.591
keyn mitglid fun di organizatsyes?

00:14:21.700 --> 00:14:22.656
 neyn.

00:14:22.591 --> 00:14:23.516
far vos?

00:14:24.147 --> 00:14:25.474
⟨bin ikh⟩ geven tsu yung.

00:14:29.766 --> 00:14:34.721
i- ayer bruder iz gevezn a, der onfirer fun Betar, in velkh⟨e⟩ shtetl?

00:14:34.575 --> 00:14:35.682
in Opalin.

00:14:37.900 --> 00:14:40.804
hot er aykh dertseylt vos di, vos zey viln...?

00:14:40.498 --> 00:14:43.175
yo, zey ⟨viln⟩ Erets-Yisroel.

00:14:45.578 --> 00:14:48.384
un in, un in LYUBOML' ⟨hobn⟩ shoyn gevezn,

00:14:48.384 --> 00:14:53.857
di yugnt zenen gegangen, m'hot geshnitn holts, m'hot ge- getrogn vaser, ⟨g- g- m'iz⟩ gelofn oparbetn

00:14:53.863 --> 00:14:56.763
⟨u⟩n, kedey me zol zey avekshikn keyn Yisroel d⟨UNK⟩.

00:14:56.614 --> 00:14:58.059
dos zaynen gevezn...

00:14:56.763 --> 00:14:58.835
s'iz geven Khalutsim, Shomrim.

00:15:04.343 --> 00:15:07.577
vos iz nokh forgekumen far der milkhome in dem,

00:15:07.853 --> 00:15:11.947
.. bikher flegn zayn in yidish dortn bay aykh, yidishe bikher?

00:15:10.519 --> 00:15:11.407
yo.

00:15:11.616 --> 00:15:12.538
s'iz geven.

00:15:12.139 --> 00:15:13.584
ir flegt leyenen?

00:15:13.303 --> 00:15:14.925
o, a sakh!

00:15:15.143 --> 00:15:17.691
ir gedenkt velkhe bikher hot ir geleyent?

00:15:17.826 --> 00:15:20.101
kh'hob geleyent l- linke bikher,

00:15:20.101 --> 00:15:21.465
alerley bikher.

00:15:21.859 --> 00:15:28.907
UNK ⟨geblibn⟩, in di bikher iz geshribn vi gut s'iz in Rusland, un m'hot yeder geklert, "o, yetst ⟨az di⟩ rusn ⟨zenen ge⟩kumen, vet zayn a lebn!"

00:15:29.605 --> 00:15:31.624
un az zey zaynen gekumen, vos iz for-...?

00:15:30.381 --> 00:15:32.805
zenen gekumen, iz geven punkt farkert.

00:15:34.768 --> 00:15:42.474
iz gevezn a yidishe teater, oder hobn geshpilt, in, di yugnt hobn geshpilt, gemakht teater aleyn in LYUBOMIR? neyn?

00:15:42.177 --> 00:15:43.909
in LYUBOML' iz geven.

00:15:44.860 --> 00:15:48.616
in LYUBOML' iz geven a kino, s'iz geven a teater. bay undz iz nisht geven in shtetl.

00:15:48.640 --> 00:15:51.368
keyn yidishe filmen hot ir nit gezen dortn?

00:15:51.407 --> 00:15:54.186
neyn. nisht geven keyn yidishe f⟨ilmen⟩.

00:16:00.148 --> 00:16:06.402
ayer mishpokhe hot gelebt, bazunder: eynike fun ayer mishpokhe zaynen gevezn in LYUBOMIR, di andere zaynen gevezn

00:16:07.033 --> 00:16:08.174
in Opalin.

00:16:07.590 --> 00:16:08.765
in Opal⟨i⟩.

00:16:12.602 --> 00:16:18.688
nu, mir veln ibergeyn tsu ⟨onheyb- un der, in der VOP-, der f-⟩ frage iz, hot ir gehert vegn

00:16:18.795 --> 00:16:23.075
Daytshland, vegn di Hitleristn, vegn di Natsis?

00:16:22.727 --> 00:16:24.425
ye, m'hot gehert.

00:16:24.769 --> 00:16:26.209
m'hot gevust az di,

00:16:26.209 --> 00:16:29.488
az di daytshn zenen, hargenen yidn.

00:16:29.697 --> 00:16:33.541
m'hot alts gevust, nor m'hot ⟨dokh⟩ gornisht gegleybt, vayl m'hot gezogt az di daytshn

00:16:33.541 --> 00:16:37.979
vos zenen geven in fertsetn yor hobn keyn yidn nisht getshepet. hot men gemeynt

00:16:37.979 --> 00:16:40.287
az di daytshn veln oykh nisht tshepen di yidn.

00:16:40.497 --> 00:16:42.270
ober s'iz geven a lignt.

00:16:43.078 --> 00:16:45.603
ir hot nit getrofn in ayer shtetl

00:16:45.677 --> 00:16:51.358
mentshn vos zaynen ⟨a- geven⟩ aroysgeshikt fun Daytshland, antlofene fun dortn oder aroysgeshikt keyn... Poyln, ye.

00:16:49.255 --> 00:16:50.598
fun Poyln.

00:16:50.993 --> 00:16:53.265
iz gekumen a sakh ⟨in d-,⟩

00:16:53.524 --> 00:16:55.647
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome ⟨zenen⟩ a sakh

00:16:55.647 --> 00:16:57.483
yidn gelofn fun Poyln.

00:16:57.523 --> 00:17:00.250
zenen zey adurkhgekumen nokh undzer shtetl, zenen gelign,

00:17:00.797 --> 00:17:04.219
oyf di poln hobn zey geshlofn in di shkoles, umedum,

00:17:04.219 --> 00:17:06.672
vos zenen antlofn fun, funem shtetl.

00:17:06.383 --> 00:17:08.706
ir meynt in nayn un draysikstn yor?

00:17:08.037 --> 00:17:09.420
nayn un draysik.

00:17:09.758 --> 00:17:14.906
I vi hot tsu zey bats- vi hot zikh tsu zey batsoygn di bafelkerung di yidishe ⟨dortn⟩?

00:17:13.588 --> 00:17:16.130
m- me fleg zey helfn, me fleg zey gibn esn,

00:17:16.643 --> 00:17:18.004
 ontsutun.

00:17:19.410 --> 00:17:21.834
ir hot nit gehat keyn bakante tsvishn zey?

00:17:19.737 --> 00:17:20.242
UNK

00:17:22.903 --> 00:17:25.056
neyn. nisht geven ⟨k-⟩...

00:17:23.915 --> 00:17:27.959
un vi hobn zikh batsoygn di sovyetn, az zey zaynen gekumen, tsu di mentshn? UNK

00:17:28.167 --> 00:17:31.334
m'hot zey avekgesh- ave- dernokh ⟨dem⟩ avekgeshikt keyn Sibir.

00:17:32.235 --> 00:17:36.093
m'hot gevolt, zey zoln krign, pasportn, zey zoln vern birger.

00:17:36.184 --> 00:17:38.756
zey hobn nisht gevolt, hot men zey bay nakht

00:17:39.289 --> 00:17:42.978
genumen oyf, ⟨ d-⟩, mashinen, un m'hot zey ale avekgefirt k- oyf Sibir.

00:17:43.845 --> 00:17:48.560
a sakh zenen geblibn lebn, a sakh ze- mentshn zenen, ⟨⟩, geshtorbn dortn.

00:17:49.262 --> 00:17:53.508
un di vos hobn genu- genumen sovyetishe pasportn zaynen geblibn lebn bay aykh?

00:17:52.519 --> 00:17:54.183
zenen geblibn arbetn.

00:17:54.662 --> 00:17:58.014
lebn zenen zey nisht geblibn; m'hot zey oykhet oysge- der daytsh hot zey geshosn.

00:17:57.615 --> 00:17:59.161
dos iz shpeter gevezn?

00:18:04.213 --> 00:18:06.569
dertseylt vos s'iz forgekumen vayter

00:18:06.930 --> 00:18:08.797
in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:18:08.483 --> 00:18:11.092
in eyn un fertsikstn yor, in der fri,

00:18:11.571 --> 00:18:13.489
⟨dem⟩ tsvey un tsvontsikstn yuni,

00:18:14.322 --> 00:18:15.728
fir a zeyger,

00:18:15.925 --> 00:18:19.336
hot UNK ongehoybn di daytshn shisn fun yener zayt Bug

00:18:19.401 --> 00:18:21.217
ariber tsun undz in shtetl.

00:18:21.679 --> 00:18:25.503
hobn shoyn gebrent di ale, kimat ale yidishe shtiber.

00:18:26.775 --> 00:18:29.739
un, u- un m'hot nisht, s'iz nisht geven vu tsu loyfn.

00:18:30.049 --> 00:18:31.733
ikh bin dem andern tog

00:18:31.733 --> 00:18:32.720
avek

00:18:32.720 --> 00:18:34.177
keyn, LYUBOML',

00:18:34.437 --> 00:18:36.371
vayl kh'hob gemeynt az dort iz shtil.

00:18:36.681 --> 00:18:39.729
ikh bin gekumen dortn, iz oykhet gevezn shoyn

00:18:39.988 --> 00:18:41.242
a shiseray

00:18:41.242 --> 00:18:46.041
un mentshn zenen gelofn. in a tsvey, dray tog zenen di daytshn geven shoyn in shtot.

00:18:46.857 --> 00:18:48.859
⟨hot zikh⟩ shoyn ongehoybn di tsores.

00:18:49.084 --> 00:18:54.292
abi zey hobn gezen a yid in der gas, hot men shoyn geshosn. di yidn hobn nisht getort shteyn in otshered nokh keyn broyt.

00:18:55.007 --> 00:18:58.376
dernokh dem hot men genumen un m'hot genumen firn oyf arbet.

00:18:59.884 --> 00:19:04.367
un dernokh dem in a, hobn zey genumen un zey hobn ge- tsunandgetribn ale yidn in a geto,

00:19:04.879 --> 00:19:10.745
un m'hot nisht getort aroysgeyn. fun finef a zeyger far nakht iz men shoyn geven in shtub un m'hot nisht getort in ergets geyn.

00:19:11.258 --> 00:19:15.116
vi hobn zey gevust az in di, in di rey far broyt shteyen yidn?

00:19:15.443 --> 00:19:16.888
vi hobn zey gevust?

00:19:15.443 --> 00:19:18.187
di yidn zenen gegangen in gele lates,

00:19:18.210 --> 00:19:20.819
tsvey: eyne fornt, un eyne oyf der pleytse.

00:19:20.910 --> 00:19:22.743
hot men gevust UNK iz a yid.

00:19:23.003 --> 00:19:25.444
oyf di late iz gevezn ongeshribn epes vos?

00:19:24.927 --> 00:19:25.765
NO.

00:19:26.698 --> 00:19:28.878
bay undz iz geven nor gele lates.

00:19:32.790 --> 00:19:34.269
yo, iz,

00:19:34.579 --> 00:19:41.053
vi lang zayt ir gevezn nit in geto?, UNK, ven hot zikh, ven zaynen ongekumen di daytshn tsu aykh?

00:19:34.855 --> 00:19:35.691
UNK

00:19:40.654 --> 00:19:46.065
di daytshn zenen ongekumen, in a tsvey, dray tog fun, azoy vi s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome.

00:19:45.582 --> 00:19:48.495
⟨un ven iz v- iz⟩ gevorn organizirt di geto bay aykh?

00:19:49.092 --> 00:19:51.718
in a por monat arum iz gevorn di geto.

00:19:52.095 --> 00:19:55.579
z- un, zey hobn genumen fun ale derfer, hobn zey arayngeshikt

00:19:55.579 --> 00:19:58.637
di yidn, fun dortn aroysgeshikt, un arayngeshikt di yidn.

00:19:58.727 --> 00:20:00.307
un ale hobn gevoynt,

00:20:00.364 --> 00:20:05.724
geven in, in di shtiber eng. s'iz nisht ⟨geve-⟩ m'iz geven krank. s'iz nisht geven keyn esn, gornisht nisht.

00:20:05.983 --> 00:20:07.614
hot der JUDENRAT

00:20:07.924 --> 00:20:14.026
gemakht in, dort vu s'iz geven a talmed-toyre, hot er gemakht a g-, a groysn kesl un m'hot gekokht a bisl SOUP,

00:20:14.607 --> 00:20:17.436
un mentshn zenen gekumen nemen a bisl SOUP tsu esn.

00:20:17.813 --> 00:20:24.135
vayl m'hot nisht getort aroysgeyn epes, koyfn bay di kristn, un di kristn hot men nisht gelozt tsugeyn tsun undz,

00:20:24.360 --> 00:20:27.155
me zol epes, ⟨f- ts-⟩ baytn tsi vos.

00:20:27.195 --> 00:20:29.349
ver s'iz aroysge⟨gan⟩ hot men geshosn.

00:20:32.005 --> 00:20:33.720
un dos hot zikh gedoyert

00:20:34.924 --> 00:20:35.998
biz

00:20:36.814 --> 00:20:38.900
dem tsvey un fertsikstn yor,

00:20:41.286 --> 00:20:44.435
yom-toyvim-tsayt. dos iz gevezn september,

00:20:44.695 --> 00:20:45.684
oktober.

00:20:48.120 --> 00:20:54.492
un di yidn zenen a sakh zikh shoyn ge- gegreyt mit farbaheltenishn, vayl m'hot gevust az m'hot oysgegrobn bay der tsigelnye

00:20:55.039 --> 00:20:58.847
groyse griber, un m'hot gezogt az dortn vet men hargenen di yidn.

00:20:59.207 --> 00:21:02.390
ober vu tsu loyfn iz nisht geven. a sakh yungvarg

00:21:02.869 --> 00:21:05.090
hobn zikh farlozt vontses

00:21:05.772 --> 00:21:11.710
un zenen avek mit a por tog tsurik. zey hobn gezogt, zey veln loyfn keyn Poyln un m'vet zey meynen az zey zenen polyakn.

00:21:12.927 --> 00:21:15.047
tsi zey zenen geblibn lebn, veys ikh nisht.

00:21:16.420 --> 00:21:19.046
un, ven zey hobn ongehoybn

00:21:19.457 --> 00:21:22.327
hargenen di yidn, hot men arumgetsoymt dos shtetl

00:21:22.327 --> 00:21:24.193
mit di Ukrayner politsey,

00:21:25.330 --> 00:21:27.174
un in der fri

00:21:27.174 --> 00:21:29.947
hobn zey ongehoybn arumloyfn iber di shtiber,

00:21:30.190 --> 00:21:33.018
aroystraybn di mentshn, un m'hot zey gefirt,

00:21:33.018 --> 00:21:34.740
s'iz geven a groyse shil,

00:21:34.881 --> 00:21:36.934
hot men zey tsunandgenumen ale in shil.

00:21:37.345 --> 00:21:40.326
dos iz gevezn shoyn in tsvey un fertsikstn yor?

00:21:39.201 --> 00:21:41.051
tsvey un fertsikstn yor.

00:21:40.467 --> 00:21:43.644
ober fun eyn un fertsikstn bizn tsvey un fertsikstn,

00:21:43.644 --> 00:21:46.012
kent ir dertseyln vegn dem lebn in geto?

00:21:46.170 --> 00:21:51.361
 vos hot ir geton, ⟨vos iz⟩ gekumen der tog in geto? mit vos hot ir zikh farnumen? UNK

00:21:50.170 --> 00:21:54.214
fleg men zikh tsu- ikh, m⟨i-,⟩ fleg men tsunandnemen arbetorers.

00:21:54.338 --> 00:21:58.790
iz gekumen eyner fun der JUDENRAT, a ⟨politsMAN⟩ a yidisher,

00:21:58.790 --> 00:22:00.964
un er fleg zey firn oyf der arbet.

00:22:01.138 --> 00:22:04.358
mir hot men genumen mit nokh mentshn stolyers

00:22:04.358 --> 00:22:07.074
un m'hot gemakht mebl far di daytshn.

00:22:07.074 --> 00:22:08.912
batsolt hot men gornisht nisht.

00:22:09.390 --> 00:22:13.681
un di, un di daytshn hobn ongehoybn khapn. s'ershte hobn zey gekhapt

00:22:13.681 --> 00:22:15.560
a por mashinen mit mener.

00:22:16.900 --> 00:22:21.981
m'hot gefregt in JUDENRAT, "v- vu hot men zey gefirt?" hobn zey gezogt, "tsu arbet." s'iz geven a lignt.

00:22:21.981 --> 00:22:23.829
vu zey zenen ahingekumen, veys men nisht.

00:22:23.953 --> 00:22:27.120
un in a khoydesh arum hobn zey gekhapt froyen,

00:22:27.244 --> 00:22:28.622
fuftsik froyen.

00:22:28.830 --> 00:22:31.459
zey hobn zey arayngevorfn in shkole, in keler,

00:22:31.459 --> 00:22:34.046
un, un dortn hobn zey gelign a gantse nakht.

00:22:34.163 --> 00:22:36.722
in der fri hot men zey aroysgenumen, m'hot zey avekgefirt.

00:22:37.369 --> 00:22:41.683
vu zey zenen ahingekumen veys men nisht. dernokh dem hot men gezogt az m'hot zey geshosn

00:22:41.689 --> 00:22:45.046
in ⟨a Skiber, dort,⟩ vald, lebn a dorf.

00:22:45.553 --> 00:22:47.707
un azoy hot zikh ongehoybn di tsores.

00:22:49.013 --> 00:22:52.365
⟨zogt mir⟩, vi hot ir gelebt? vi hot ir gekrogn vos tsu esn?

00:22:53.400 --> 00:22:55.756
tsu esn iz n- iz nisht geven gornisht nisht.

00:22:55.763 --> 00:22:58.592
mayn shvester fleg mir shikn fun Opalin

00:22:58.918 --> 00:23:02.897
mit a, mit a mentshn... di mentshn vos zey hobn gearbet, Opaliner...

00:23:02.897 --> 00:23:05.004
a bisl kartoflyes mit a broyt,

00:23:05.078 --> 00:23:08.548
un dos hot men gehat oyf UNK esn. un me fleg nemen a bisl SOUP

00:23:09.330 --> 00:23:11.011
bay der JUDENRAT.

00:23:11.794 --> 00:23:14.001
keyn esn hot men nisht gehat, un keyn gelt

00:23:14.001 --> 00:23:16.990
iz gornisht geven vos tsu koyfn, un m'hot nisht gekent koyfn.

00:23:16.941 --> 00:23:20.664
vi hobn zikh tsu aykh batsien di politseyen vos zaynen gevezn, di yidishe?

00:23:21.328 --> 00:23:24.112
di yidishe politsey iz oykhet geven genug shlekht.

00:23:24.754 --> 00:23:27.177
⟨ah,⟩ zey, zey flegn nisht lozn aroysgeyn

00:23:27.177 --> 00:23:30.047
fun geto, me zol, epes geyn, epes nemen.

00:23:31.588 --> 00:23:33.641
zey flegn kumen un me zol gibn,

00:23:33.715 --> 00:23:37.472
 d- vayl di daytshn zogn, zey hobn bafoyln, me zol gibn dos gold,

00:23:37.545 --> 00:23:40.309
me zol gibn leder, me zol gibn skhoyres.

00:23:40.309 --> 00:23:42.224
flegn zey araynkumen in di shtiber

00:23:42.224 --> 00:23:44.981
un, tsvingen, me zol yeder eyner gibn.

00:23:47.957 --> 00:23:51.485
me fleg tsunandnemen far, far di daytshn di ale zakhn.

00:23:53.053 --> 00:23:56.543
fun ayer mishpokhe, a teyl fun aykh zaynen gevezn

00:23:56.543 --> 00:23:57.823
in LYUBOMIR,

00:23:58.437 --> 00:24:00.118
un di andere zaynen geven in ⟨Apoli⟩,

00:24:00.681 --> 00:24:01.670
in ⟨Apolin⟩?

00:24:02.301 --> 00:24:03.915
ver iz iz gevezn in ⟨Apolin⟩?

00:24:04.360 --> 00:24:06.328
in Opalin iz geven der bruder,

00:24:07.718 --> 00:24:09.163
un di shvester,

00:24:09.793 --> 00:24:11.660
un der onkl mit di kinder.

00:24:13.050 --> 00:24:15.254
un in LYUBOML' iz gevezn,

00:24:15.430 --> 00:24:16.959
mayne tsvey brider

00:24:17.269 --> 00:24:18.680
un di,

00:24:19.969 --> 00:24:22.626
un di tyotyes un di ⟨b-⟩

00:24:22.855 --> 00:24:25.373
ale, di, vos zenen geven, vos zey hobn gevoynt dortn.

00:24:28.103 --> 00:24:33.885
un zey iz, hot men oykh getsvungen tsu geyn tsu der arbet, ayere brider, di mumes ayere?

00:24:33.553 --> 00:24:35.229
me fleg khapn, ⟨⟩,

00:24:35.229 --> 00:24:38.448
vemen m'hot getrofn, ge- hot men gekhapt in di shtiber.

00:24:38.448 --> 00:24:41.816
m'hot aroysgefirt, me zol, vayl s'iz opgebrent gevorn di shtot,

00:24:42.058 --> 00:24:44.296
me zol reynikn dos plats.

00:24:44.421 --> 00:24:47.056
flegn zey farnemen mit, mit lopetes, mit

00:24:47.056 --> 00:24:49.504
grablyes un m'hot gereynikt, di gas

00:24:49.504 --> 00:24:51.739
dortn, vu s'iz geven farbrent di shtiber.

00:24:52.065 --> 00:24:55.598
un a- ale tog hot men azoy gegangen un m'hot genumen di yidn oyf der arbet,

00:24:55.598 --> 00:24:57.037
me zol makhn dem veg,

00:24:57.432 --> 00:24:59.552
zey zoln kenen forn mit di mashinen.

00:25:06.443 --> 00:25:09.443
iz in geto gevezn epes a

00:25:09.443 --> 00:25:11.584
religyozer lebn?

00:25:11.978 --> 00:25:16.731
mentshn flegn davnen, flegn zikh klaybn oyf yom-toyvim oder oyf shabes?

00:25:18.627 --> 00:25:23.233
s'iz geven yidn vos zenen nokh geganen davenen a bisl, BUT ⟨in,⟩ der ershter tsayt.

00:25:23.638 --> 00:25:26.754
eyn mol hob ikh gezen, ven m'hot gedavnt, s'iz geven rosheshone,

00:25:26.845 --> 00:25:29.392
un eyn daytsh mit a groyser hunt

00:25:29.848 --> 00:25:31.664
iz ge- arayn in shil arayn,

00:25:31.705 --> 00:25:35.169
un hot zikh gedreyt dortn, un er iz avekgegan, hot nisht getshepet nokh di mentshn.

00:25:35.169 --> 00:25:38.397
dos iz geven shoyn nisht lang farn umbrengen dem geto.

00:25:42.167 --> 00:25:44.928
ir zayt, ir zayt nit gegangen in shul?

00:25:42.217 --> 00:25:43.217
mentshn...

00:25:46.453 --> 00:25:47.962
ikh bin gegan in shil.

00:25:47.753 --> 00:25:48.911
gegangen in shul?

00:25:48.917 --> 00:25:52.179
⟨VOT I v- in⟩ di tsayt ven ir zayt geven in geto shoyn,

00:25:52.179 --> 00:25:55.065
iz gevezn, geven azelkhe yom-toyvim vi yom-kiper?

00:25:55.498 --> 00:25:57.635
in yom-kiper zayt ir gegangen...?

00:25:56.393 --> 00:25:57.703
m'hot gearbet.

00:25:58.214 --> 00:26:03.857
sh- rosheshone, yom-kiper, hot men gearbet. m'hot nisht gezogt az, me zol nisht arbetn, vayl

00:26:03.857 --> 00:26:06.866
m'hot moyre gehat, di daytshn zoln ⟨h-⟩ hargenen.

00:26:07.952 --> 00:26:13.121
ikh b- ikh hob eyn mol geshtanen in, in, in gas un geleyent a, s'iz geven a,

00:26:13.121 --> 00:26:15.387
⟨ot dos⟩, a af- a afish.

00:26:15.732 --> 00:26:19.348
iz adurkhgegan a daytsh, hot er mir gegibn tsvey patshn in ponem,

00:26:19.348 --> 00:26:21.243
far derfar vos ikh bin geshtanen

00:26:21.452 --> 00:26:24.121
oyf, oyfn trotuar vu er geyt adurkh.

00:26:24.405 --> 00:26:26.364
dos iz geven mayn ershter onheyb

00:26:26.532 --> 00:26:27.825
fun di daytshn.

00:26:27.240 --> 00:26:29.006
dos iz nokh far dem geto?

00:26:29.400 --> 00:26:32.380
NO, shoyn in, in geto.

00:26:33.838 --> 00:26:35.355
m'hot nisht getort shteyn

00:26:35.355 --> 00:26:36.999
vu di daytshn zenen gegangen.

00:26:36.842 --> 00:26:38.743
ayer geto iz geven...

00:26:37.399 --> 00:26:39.047
un eyn mol,

00:26:39.880 --> 00:26:42.450
a por vokhn shoyn nokhn onheyb ⟨fun der⟩ milkhome,

00:26:42.450 --> 00:26:45.898
hobn zey tsunandgerufn ale yidn, zey zoln kumen in park.

00:26:47.136 --> 00:26:51.838
dort hobn zey genumen, un oysgekloybn finef, di beste, di shenste yidn.

00:26:52.063 --> 00:26:54.774
zey hobn gezogt az di yidn hobn geharget di daytshn.

00:26:55.523 --> 00:27:00.157
un m'hot zey arumgeringlt mit av-, avtomatn, di daytshn, un m'hot zey aropgefirt

00:27:00.231 --> 00:27:03.330
funem mark biz, s'iz geven dort a barg barn kino,

00:27:03.505 --> 00:27:06.114
un dort hot men zey oysgeshosn ale.

00:27:06.694 --> 00:27:09.287
ikh bin oykh gevezn, ober ikh bin antlofn

00:27:09.445 --> 00:27:12.336
fun dem, dem miting vos iz gevezn.

00:27:12.336 --> 00:27:14.542
un mayn onkl hot men derharget.

00:27:14.980 --> 00:27:17.600
un dem andern tog iz gekumen di yidn,

00:27:17.600 --> 00:27:20.913
un m'hot tsunandgenumen zey oyf a fur, un m'hot zey avekgefirt in heylikn ort.

00:27:25.847 --> 00:27:29.520
a sakh yidn zenen, ⟨, f-⟩ kranke geshtorbn in di shtiber,

00:27:29.762 --> 00:27:32.675
vayl s'iz nisht geven keyn dokter un s'iz nisht geven vos tsu esn,

00:27:32.715 --> 00:27:34.565
un m'hot gornisht gekent helfn zey.

00:27:34.555 --> 00:27:37.925
keyn yidishe doktoyrim zaynen nit gevezn in geto dortn?

00:27:41.153 --> 00:27:45.056
un der JUDENRAT hot nit organizirt UNK doktoyrim,

00:27:45.056 --> 00:27:47.074
krankn-shvester, zey zoln helfn?

00:27:46.452 --> 00:27:48.606
⟨s'iz, s'iz, s'iz⟩ gornisht geven.

00:27:50.012 --> 00:27:52.216
m'iz gezitsn farmakht in di shtiber

00:27:52.307 --> 00:27:54.149
un m'hot moyre gehat aroystsugeyn,

00:27:54.754 --> 00:27:56.598
vayl ale mol hot men gekhapt.

00:27:56.598 --> 00:27:58.999
un yedn eyner hot zikh gemakht in der shtub

00:27:58.999 --> 00:28:00.401
a farbaheltenish.

00:28:00.998 --> 00:28:05.906
az m'iz arayngekumen, hot men gemeynt az m'vet nisht tshepen di froyen, un zey hobn gekhapt di froyen oykhet.

00:28:06.567 --> 00:28:07.945
froyen, mener.

00:28:11.224 --> 00:28:16.162
eyn mol hot, hot mir genumen der balebos fun shtot. kh'hob geshnitn holts bay im.

00:28:16.860 --> 00:28:20.882
hot men gebrengt a mashin mit yidishe zakhn fun Shatsk, funem rayon,

00:28:20.882 --> 00:28:22.575
vos m'hot oysgeharget di yidn.

00:28:22.716 --> 00:28:26.068
hot er mir geheysn tsunandleygn oyf di polkes

00:28:26.260 --> 00:28:28.020
zakhn. hob ikh gel- gezen,

00:28:28.020 --> 00:28:30.863
s'iz geven taleysim, s'iz geven shoyn neymashinen,

00:28:30.863 --> 00:28:32.767
kleyne shikhelekh fun kinder.

00:28:33.162 --> 00:28:36.480
hob, hob ikh shoyn gezogt di mentshn az m'hot shoyn oysgeharget in shtetl.

00:28:37.009 --> 00:28:39.568
dos iz geven nisht vayt a shtetl fun LYUBOML'.

00:28:39.726 --> 00:28:41.137
vi hot geheysn di shtetl?

00:28:40.823 --> 00:28:41.899
Shatsk.

00:28:41.899 --> 00:28:43.252
shtetl Shatsk.

00:28:44.097 --> 00:28:47.644
mir raysn zikh iber oyf a vayle tsu baytn dem TAPE.

00:28:50.634 --> 00:28:51.634
UNK
